# Welcome!

This is your first blog post. You can write in **markdown** and it will be automatically converted to HTML.

## Features

This simple PHP static site generator supports:

* Markdown parsing
* Frontmatter for metadata (title, date, etc.)
* Clean URLs
* JSON API endpoints

## Code Examples

You can include `inline code` or code blocks:

```
function hello() {
    return "Hello, world!";
}
```

## Links

You can add [links to other pages](/blog/why-simple-tools-are-better) easily.

---

Edit this file or create new `.md` files in the `/blog` directory to add more posts!
